dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: The Future Land Use data set form the basis of the county's land use strategy.  The information contained in the dataset is used for the planning of future development activities in the County. Area designations include residential, commercial, manufacturing, and forest uses, among others.Derivative data is routinely refreshed as the master data set is updated.
